14:
A crude iron sword & shield that,
despite its mass-produced
quality, packs quite a punch.
18:
A sword & shield of fine steel,
with improved durability and
power for more demanding hunts.
22:
A lavish sword & shield of rare
steel able to split even the
hardest of shells with ease.
25:
The Nergigante scales on this
sword & shield continually regrow,
promising unending pain to foes.
27:
Forged from Nergigante parts,
it severs the chain of grief
created by the sinner's acts.
29:
Residual heat in the Rathalos
parts used in this sword & shield
grants it a searing strike.
32:
This sword & shield's blade carries
the flame of a Rathalos within it,
forever glowing a dull red.
36:
Well-beloved by hunters, this sword
& shield uses its crushing weight
to mimic much larger weapons.
39:
New forging techniques have been
used to give this iron sword & shield
a water element coating.
43:
Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and water
element of this sword & shield.
47:
This icy, keenly honed Legiana
sword & shield hums as it cuts
graceful arcs and figures.
50:
A Legiana sword & shield. Cut,
and may any foe your brand bites
suffer a hailstorm of icy pillars.
53:
Bearing a budding thorn motif,
this Rathian sword is a work of
art as well as a fine weapon.
56:
A queen of legend survived a
coup thanks to this Pink Rathian
rapier's protection.
59:
A decadent sword & shield
lavished in rich, lustrous
Paolumu hide.
62:
A sword & shield swathed in luxe
Paolumu hide so lustrous it appears
dew-dappled. For elegant slaying.
66:
The Pukei-Pukei's colorful down
hides potent venom, making this
a lot less cute than it looks.
70:
The venom-soaked down of the
Pukei-Pukei covering this blade
bristles at the sight of prey.
74:
Steeped in virulent Great Girros
toxin, this sword's bite
swiftly paralyzes its prey.
77:
The numbing sting of paralytic
toxin from this Great Girros sword
leaves prey defenseless.
81:
A sword & shield made from easily
obtainable bone. Rough-hewn, but
a sturdy friend to new hunters.
85:
Made from the densest of bones,
this sword & shield offers greater
power with the same ease of use.
89:
A sword & shield made of modified
bone. Each primal slash is
capable of cleaving solid rock.
92:
Lavished in sharp Radobaan bone
shards, this sword scrapes the
flesh from its prey.
95:
A bone-chilling sword & shield
that embodies both the destructive
and defensive power of the Radobaan.
99:
Wrapped in supple Jagras hide,
this sword & shield fits firmly in
the user's grip.
103:
Lavish use of butter-soft Jagras
hide makes this sword & shield
feel like an extension of its user.
107:
New forging techniques have been
used to give this bone sword & shield
a thunder element coating.
110:
Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and thunder
element of this sword & shield.
114:
Adding Barroth parts only made
this sword & shield more stark and
brutish...in a good way.
118:
Imbued with the destructive
might of a Barroth, each slash
carves new scars into the earth.
122:
A sword & shield wrapped
in hide tempered hard as iron in
the searing breath of an Anjanath.
125:
A pulsing heat builds within the blade
from this Anjanath sword & shield set
with every bloodthirsty strike.
128:
A dragon element sword & shield
hewn from bone, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
132:
This Kirin sword & shield shines
with divine light as its blade
crackles with electricity.
134:
A Kirin sword & shield. Even a single
slash from the blade contains enough
might to awaken a thunder god.
137:
A dragon element sword & shield
forged in iron, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
140:
An emblem of the crimson flame
king, this Teostra sword & shield
is the key to hell's burning gates.
143:
A Xeno'jiiva sword & shield, lord
among treasures. Its pitiless
judgment severs all before it.
145:
A powerful sword & shield that
channels the bloodthirst of
Deviljho into every swing.
148:
A Kulve Taroth sword & shield
with unknown traits. Its true
potential has yet to be realized.
152:
A Kulve Taroth sword & shield
that utilizes other monster parts
for research purposes.
163:
A Kulve Taroth sword & shield
that possesses new properties
due to clever material utilization.
174:
A Kulve Taroth sword & shield that
fully harnesses the hidden power
of the materials used to create it.
178:
A hidden power seeps from
this Lunastra sword & shield,
as if a soul is trapped inside.
180:
This Lunastra sword & shield was
forged in hellfire. Sometimes
guards its user from fatal blows.

This Lunastra sword & shield
resonates with Nergigante parts
to give a chance for regeneration.
184:
This Lunastra sword & shield
resonates with Xeno'jiiva parts
to help keep your weapon sharp.
187:
A unique sword & shield made from
the gold of Kulve Taroth. Houses
the true might of the goddess within.
195:
A sword made of silver possessing
the power to ward off evil.
Ideal for slaying monsters.
198:
Crafted specifically for the Defense
Corps, its high-performance
output is thanks to modern tech.
204:
Using only the rarest of metals,
this weapon can slash through
even the toughest defense.
208:
The end of days is nigh. This
Ruiner Nergigante sword &
shield sever sin from sinner.
211:
Forged in Azure Rathalos breath,
this sword & shield marks its user

An ancient, light-bringing
sword & shield blessed by the
Gold Queen and Silver King.
215:
Made of ore compressed to the
hardness of elder dragon scales,
this blade is the envy of all.
221:
A Barioth sword of extreme cold.

freeze prey from the inside.

Cut deep, and let the Shrieking
Legiana chill your blade to the
edge of absolute zero.
231:
The sword of a noble queen
who braved the path of thorns,
leaving red flowers as testament.
233:
A luxurious, high-end Paolumu
sword with elegant plumage
for the distinguished hunter.
236:
A Nightshade Paolumu sword
& shield. The beautiful black fur
glistens with the blood of its foes.
239:
Top-grade Pukei-Pukei down steeped
in a virulent venom grant this
sword & shield its lethal bite.
242:
Contrary to its blazing colors,
this Coral Pukei-Pukei sword
& shield drains its prey of heat.
245:
Caution is needed when wielding
this Great Girros sword, for it
contains a potent paralytic toxin.
248:
A Nargacuga sword & shield.
The strange texture of its blade
is said to conceal bloodstains.
252:
A sword & shield made of only
the rarest bones. Powerful
enough to cleave steel.
256:
The icy edge of this Velkhana
sword & shield freezes the final
cries of prey in their throat.
259:
With its added layer of thick bones,
this Radobaan sword mercilessly
scrapes the flesh from its prey.
262:
The acid flowing from this Acidic
Glavenus sword & shield weakens
its prey from within.
265:
This Great Jagras sword & shield
handle so easily they feel like
an extension of one's arms.
268:
Modeled after a Tigrex claw.
One swing pulverizes the
enemy with an enormous roar.
273:
A Zinogre sword & shield.
Its strikes fall like arcs of
lightning, searing its prey.
277:
Nothing can stand in the way of
the dark power contained in this
Stygian Zinogre sword & shield.
280:
This Glavenus sword & shield
stoke the flame of a hunter's
passion to sear all before them.
283:
Stout and unyielding, this
Barroth sword & shield carve
at the earth with each blow.
286:
Replicating the unbridled force
of a Brachydios, this sword
destroys everything it touches.
289:
A Raging Brachydios sword
that stirs the earth with explosive
tirades, devouring all in sight.
293:
This Fulgur Anjanath sword
& shield strike with the speed
of the lightning within them.
297:
A dragon element sword & shield
hewn from bone, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
300:
Purify the sullied with this
Shara Ishvalda sword & shield,
which balances fury and mercy.
304:
Containing the mysterious powers
of a Kirin, this sword cleaves the
earth with a crash of thunder.
306:
Each slash of this Namielle
sword & shield drags its victim's
consciousness into the abyss.
312:
Take up this Savage Deviljho
sword & shield and give in to
the rising urge to slaughter.
314:
A club-shaped Rajang sword,
designed to release lightning
when swung.
316:
A Furious Rajang sword &
shield for those already on
the warpath.
318:
A bewitching sword & shield made
from Alatreon parts. Its formless
voice lures warriors to darkness.
324:
A bewitching black Brute Tigrex
sword & shield that crushes
all who feel its claw.
327:
Bestowed upon guild knights with
stellar achievements. The sublime
glow is a source of pride.
330:
A silver Frostfang Barioth sword &
shield enveloped by a sharp cold.
Proof of the hoarfrost's keeper.
332:
The ultimate power in this Fatalis

342:
A sword & shield made from Safi'jiiva
parts. Awaken its hidden potential
by using unique materials.
